{"word":"G4768 - στυγνάζω - stygnázō - stoog-nad'-zo - Lower","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">στυγνάζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">stygnázō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">stoog-nad'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Lower</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - மந்தாரமாயிரு, மனமடி"},{"paragraph":"to be sad, to be sorrowful"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the same as <a href=\"#/G4767 - στυγνητός - stygnētós - stoog-nay-tos'/4767\">G4767</a>; to <i>render gloomy</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>glower</i> (<i>be overcast</i> with clouds, or <i>sombreness</i> of speech): - lower, be sad.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}